main_body:
1. The amount of the production aid shall be such as to offset the difference between the Community offer price for tinned pineapples and the prices charged by third country supplier countries of these products.
2. The Council, acting by a qualified majority on a proposal from the Commission, shall fix the following every year in time for the start of the marketing year:    (a) the amount of the aid;
(b) the minimum price level referred to in Article 3.
